\id 1TH Bible in Fouta-Jalon Pular
\mt1 ∆ÅATAKURU PUULUSA ARANURU HAA E ∆ÅE TESALONII ∆ÅEN
\c 1
\p 
\v 1 Immorde e an min Puulusa, wondude e Silaasi e Timotee, haa e ngal *moftal wongal Tesalonii, humondir…ìe e Alla Baabaajo on e Iisaa Almasiihu Joomi on. Yo mo∆¥∆¥ere e …ìuttu wonan on.
\s1 Fii Anditangol …ìe Tesalonii …ìen Gom…óinal ma…ì…ìe ngal
\p 
\v 2 Me…óen duumii e jarnugol Alla fii mon on fow, e me…óen anditude fii mon on fow e nder torndeeji amen …óin.
\v 3 Me…óen anditude soono woo yeeso Alla, on Ben men, kuu…óe gom…óinal mon ngal e golle giggol mon ngol e tama'u mo cator…óon e Iisaa Almasiihu Joomi men on.
\v 4 Me…óen andi, yo musi…ì…ìe …ìe Alla yi…ói, ko on su…ìaa…ìe,
\v 5 ko fii Kibaaru Mo∆¥∆¥o mo men woni fe…≤…≤inde on, men addiranaali on mo kongol tun, kono ko wondude e bawgal e *Ruuhu Senii…óo on e hoolaare mawnde. E hi…óon andi-le no men wondirnoo e mon fii nafa mon.
\v 6 Onon kadi on …≤embii men, on …≤embii Joomi on. Hay e nder tampereeji mon …óuu…óu…ói …óin, on ja…ìirii daaluyee on weltaare iwrunde e Ruuhu Senii…óo on.
\v 7 Ko …óun wa…ói, on wonii …ìe gom…óin…ìe …ìen Masedonii e Akaaya fow …≤embinta.
\v 8 Ko fii daaluyee Joomiraa…óo on lollirii immorde ka mon, hinaa non e hoore Masedonii e Akaaya tun, kono gom…óinal mon ngal e Alla andike nokkeeli …óin fow, haa ka tawata hewtaa ka men wowla fii mun.
\v 9 No sifeede fii ja…ì…ìo ngo men ja…ì…ìaa ka mon ngon, e ko honno tuubiran…óon Alla, yilti…óon e …ìaawo sanamuuji fii rewugol Alla Wuuru…óo Goongaajo on,
\v 10 e fii habbagol ka kammuuli on ∆Åi…ó…óo makko, mo o immintini e hakkunde may…ìe …ìen, …óun ko Iisaa, on Jattin…óo en tikkere aroyaynde nden.
\c 2
\s1 Fii Golle Puulusa …óen e hakkunde …ìe Tesalonii …ìen
\p 
\v 1 Hi…óon andi onon tigi, yo musi…ì…ìe, ardu amen ndun ka mon wonaali meerenteeru.
\v 2 Kono …ìawto men tampude, men tampinee e ndee saare wi'eteende Filipii, wano andir…óon non, men ∆¥etti hoolaare e Alla men on fii fe…≤…≤inangol on Kibaaru Mo∆¥∆¥o Alla on e nder tippiro mawngo.
\v 3 E hoore …óun, waajuuji amen …óin hinaa e palji iwri, maa e anniyeeji bon…ói, maa e ∆¥oyre,
\v 4 kono …ìay Alla tawii me…óen foddi e halfineede Kibaaru Mo∆¥∆¥o on, ko …óun wa…ói si men yewtirtaa no welirta yim…ìe …ìen, kono ko no welirta Alla, on ndarndotoo…óo …ìer…óe amen …óen.
\v 5 E hoore …óun, hi…óon andi men …óayniraali on mantirgol kongu…ói, miile kadi ardaaki men, Alla ko seedee e …óun.
\v 6 E men …óa…ì…ìaali kadi yo yim…ìe …ìen teddin men, woni onon, woni heddii…ìe …ìen.
\v 7 Hay si men waawayno hollude on mbawdi sabu ko men *sahaabaa…ìe *Almasiihu on, men wa…óaali …óun. Kono fewndo men wondi e mon, men holli on newaare, wano neene dankorta …ìi…ì…ìe mun.
\v 8 E nder giggol ngol men joganii on ngol, me…óen yi…óunoo ye…óugol on Kibaaru Mo∆¥∆¥o Alla on, kono kadi ngurndan amen …óan tigi, hakkee ko men yi…ói on.
\v 9 Onon on anditii, yo musi…ì…ìe, golle amen …óen e yangi amen kin fewndo men fe…≤…≤inannoo on Kibaaru Mo∆¥∆¥o Alla on, men gollirno jemma e …≤alorma, fii wota men wonan hay gooto e mon dongal.
\p 
\v 10 Ko on seedee, Alla kadi ko seedee, men wonirno e noone laa…ìu…óo e no feewiri e no felnoraa telen-ma mon, onon gom…óin…ìe …ìen.
\v 11 Hi…óon andi kadi men woniranno kala e mon wano baaba woniranta fay…ìe mun.
\v 12 Men waajino on, men wakkilini on, men jeeji on yo on wuurir noone no welirta Alla, on Noddu…óo on ka *laamateeri mun e ka mangu mun.
\p 
\v 13 E hino ko men duumori e jarnugol Alla kon: e nder ja…ìugol mon daaluyee mo men fe…≤…≤inannoo on on, on ja…ìiraano mo wa iwru…óo e ne…ó…óanke, kono on ja…ìirno mo wa daaluyee Alla, no o woniri haqiiqa non, ko on daaluyee woni gollude e mon onon gom…óin…ìe …ìen.
\v 14 On …ìanginno …óun, yo musi…ì…ìe, e nder …≤embugol mon *mofte Alla won…óe ka diiwal Yahuuda …óen, …óe tawata ko Iisaa Almasiihu on jeyi, ko fii onon kadi on tampuno e juu…óe …≤okondoo…ìe mon …ìen sifa tampereeji …ói *Yahuudiyankee…ìe …ìen tampinnoo …óen mofte …óin.
\v 15 Ko …ìen wari Iisaa Joomi on, wari annabaa…ìe …ìen, cukkii men, …óun ko …ìen …ìe welataa Alla, won…ìe ay…ìe yim…ìe …ìen fow.
\v 16 Hi…ìe fanni men yewtugol …ìe wonaa Yahuudiyanke …ìen fii wota …ìen dande, ko nii …ìe jokkiri hebbingol junuubaaji ma…ì…ìe …óin. Kono tikkere Alla nden sakkitori nangugol …ìe.
\s1 Fii no Puulusa Nuliri Timotee
\p 
\v 17 Menen, telen-ma amen yo musi…ì…ìe, e nder ko men seedunoo e mon kon e nder saa'ihun e …ìandu, kono hinaa e …ìernde, hakkee ko men marnoo faale tii…óu…óo fii yi'itugol on, men etino fii …óun fota.
\v 18 Ko …óun wa…ói si men faalano yahude ka mon, tentinii min Puulusa, mi etino …óun …ìuri nde wootere. Kono Ibuliisa hanni men.
\v 19 E hara hinaa onon woni tama'u amen on e weltaare amen nden e *meetelol darja amen on yeeso Iisaa Joomi men on …≤ande ardu makko ndun?
\v 20 Hiiyii, ko onon woni darja amen on e weltaare amen nden!
\c 3
\p 
\v 1 Ko …óun wa…ói si men wawtaano hande kadi habbagol ko …ìuri nii, men tawi no …ìurani men ka men wona menen tun ka saare Atiina,
\v 2 men imminana on oo musi…ó…óo amen innetee…óo Timotee, on wondi…ó…óo amen e nder golle Alla …óen e hoore fe…≤…≤ingol Kibaaru Mo∆¥∆¥o *Almasiihu on. Men fawi mo tii…óingol on e wakkilingol on ka gom…óinal mon,
\v 3 fii wota hay gooto dilline e nder tampereeji fewndii…ói …óin. Ko fii onon tigi hi…óon andi ko …óun muuyana…óen.
\v 4 Fewndo ko men wonnoo takko mon, men wowlanayno on wonde en he…ìay satteendeeji, ko …óun woni ko hewti, hi…óon andi.
\v 5 Ko …óun wa…ói, …ìay mi waawataano habbaade hande kadi, mi imminii Timotee fii humpitagol gom…óinal mon ngal, mi…óo hulunoo wota taw no gasa hara jarribotoo…óo on faljinii on, tawa golle amen …óen wonii meere.
\p 
\v 6 Awa Timotee ko e hewtitude woni ka amen iwrude ka mon, o addoranii men kibaaru mo∆¥∆¥o fii gom…óinal mon ngal e giggol mon ngol. O innii men, tigi-tigi on, hi…óon joganii men maande mo∆¥∆¥ere, awa kadi hi…óon himmani yi'ugol men, wano men himmirani yi'ugol on non.
\v 7 E hoore …óun, e nder satteende amen nden fow e tampere amen nden, yo musi…ì…ìe, men wakkilinaama sabu gom…óinal mon ngal.
\v 8 Jooni non hi…óen wuuri, ko fii hi…óon tabiti few e Joomiraa…óo on.
\v 9 E hara ko honno men waawata jarnirde Alla fii mon, fii ndee weltaare nde weltin…óon men yeeso makko fow?
\v 10 Ko …óun wa…ói, jemma e …≤alorma me…óen toraade mo e nder tentingol fii yo o newnan men yi'itugol on, timmintina ko ≈ãakki e gom…óinal mon ngal kon.
\p 
\v 11 Yo Alla Ben men on tigi, e Iisaa Joomi men on, udditan men laawol haa ka mon.
\v 12 Awa kadi yo Joomiraa…óo on hebbin giggol hakkundeeji mon haa fe∆¥∆¥ita, e telen-ma yim…ìe …ìen fow, hara kadi ko sifa giggol ngol men joganii on ngol.
\v 13 Yo o tabintinir nii …ìer…óe mon …óen fii no woniron laa…ìu…ìe e …ìe felnaaki yeeso Alla Baabaajo men on, ka …≤alaande nde Iisaa Joomi men on aroyta e mun wondude e laa…ìu…ìe mun …ìen fow.
\c 4
\s1 Fii Wuurirgol no Welirta Alla
\p 
\v 1 Ka rawnoode, yo musi…ì…ìe, on andirii men ko honno gasirton wonirde fii no weliron Alla, e hin-le ko non wonir…óon. Jooni men torike on, men jeejii, sabu humondiral men e Iisaa Joomi on, …ìeydee yaarude yeeso soono woo e …óen ba≈ã≈ãe.
\v 2 Ko fii hi…óon andi janndeeji …ói men janni on …óin immorde e Iisaa Joomi on.
\v 3 Ko Alla faalaa ko yo on laato laa…ìu…ìe, e fii yo on wo…ó…óito jinaa,
\v 4 e yo mo kala e mon waawu jogitaade …ìandu mun ndun e nder laa…ìal e teddungal,
\v 5 e …ìaawo accugol faaleeji wonkii foola …óun, wano …ìe gom…óinaa andaa Alla …ìen gerdata non.
\v 6 E telen-ma …óun, wota hay gooto bonnu musi…ó…óo mun maa huutora mo ∆¥oyre, ko fii Joomiraa…óo on yo…ìay sifa …óin noone ellaaji fow. Hari men wowlaniino on …óun, men hajike on e …óun.
\v 7 Ko fii Alla noddiraali en wuurirgol angal laa…ìal, kono ko wuurirgol laa…ìal.
\v 8 Ko …óun wa…ói, on bugitii…óo ngal gandal, haray hinaa ne…ó…óo o bugitii, kono ko Alla, on Ye…óu…óo on *Ruuhu mun Senii…óo on.
\p 
\v 9 E telen-ma giggol si…ó…óankaaku musi…ì…ìe gom…óin…ìe …ìen, on hatonjinaa e windaneede fii …óun, ko fii Alla tigi wawnii on yi…óindirgol.
\v 10 Ko …óun kadi won…óon wa…óude e fee musi…ì…ìe men …ìen fow e nder Masedonii no didori, kono men wakkilinii on, yo musi…ì…ìe, …ìeydugol kadi.
\v 11 Himmanon wuurirgol …ìuttu, jokkon haajuuji mon …óin tigi, golliron juu…óe mon …óen, wano men yamiriri on non.
\v 12 ∆äun ko fii no woniron feewu…ìe e telen-ma …ìe gom…óinaa …ìen, hara on wonataa dongal hay gooto.
\s1 Fii Artugol Iisaa
\p 
\v 13 Men faalaaka, yo musi…ì…ìe, yo on ronku andude fii may…ìe …ìen, fii wota on he…ìu sokola, wano …ìeya …ìe alaa tama'u …ìen.
\v 14 Ko …óun wa…ói, …ìay hi…óen gom…óini Iisaa maayii, awa kadi o immintinaama, hi…óen gom…óini kadi Alla artiray maayu…ìe no gom…óini Iisaa …ìen wondude e makko.
\v 15 Awa e hino ko men wi'ata on, …óun non ko e kongol Joomi on iwri: enen wur…ìe …ìen, luttitu…ìe haa …≤ande ardu Joomi on, en adotaako may…ìe …ìen artireede.
\v 16 Ko fii, Joomi on tigi iwray ka kammu, tippoda e yamiroore ewnaande e hawa malaa'ikaajo maw…óo e hito *liital Alla ngal. Onsay ko maayu…ìe no gom…óini *Almasiihu on …ìen adetee immintineede.
\v 17 ∆Åawto …óun, enen wur…ìe luttitay…ìe …ìen, en ∆¥ettidete e ma…ì…ìe ka nder duule, fii fottoygol e Joomi on ka weeyo. Onsay en wonday e Joomi on haa poomaa.
\v 18 Awa wakkilindiree rewrude e …óii kongu…ói.
\c 5
\p 
\v 1 Fii …≤alaa…óe …óen e saa'iiji …óin, on hatonjinaa e windaneede fii …óun, yo musi…ì…ìe.
\v 2 Ko fii onon tigi hi…óon andi few …≤alaande Joomi on arday wa nde ngujjo no ara jemma.
\v 3 Nde yim…ìe wi'i: ¬´∆Åuttu ngun tabitii, tawa kadi masiibo alaa!¬ª, ko onsay halakuyee on arata he…≤a, yana e ma…ì…ìe wa nde ≈ãata fi…ói debbo reeduujo, hara …ìe da…óataa-le few.
\p 
\v 4 Kono onon, yo musi…ì…ìe, on alaa e nder niwre nden haa ka nden …≤alaande juhira on wa ngujjo.
\v 5 On fow ko on …ìi…ì…ìe ndaygu ngun e …ìi…ì…ìe …≤alorma on. Hinaa en …ìe jemma on maa niwre nden.
\v 6 Awa, wota en …óaanor wa …ìeya, kono wattanen yiila, wonen hakkilan…ìe.
\v 7 ∆äaanotoo…ìe …ìen …óaanoto jemma, mandiloo…ìe …ìen ko jemma mandilirta.
\v 8 Kono enen yim…ìe …≤alorma …ìen, wonen hakkilan…ìe, …ìorno…óen hiwitorgo gom…óinal ngal e giggol ngol, hippo…óen kunnawal tama'u kisiyee on.
\v 9 Ko fii Alla muuyanaali en tikkere makko nden, kono ko fii no he…ìiren kisiyee rewrude e Iisaa Almasiihu Joomi men on,
\v 10 on may…óo fii men, fii, woni hi…óen …óaanii, woni en …óaanaaki, no wuuridiren e makko.
\v 11 Awa, wakkilindiree, tii…óindiron, wano won…óon warrude non fewndo …óoo.
\s1 Fii Yamirooje Sakkitore …óen e Salminaango ngon
\p 
\v 12 Men torike on, yo musi…ì…ìe, anditanee won…ìe gollude hakkunde mon …ìen, …ìen …ìe Joomiraa…óo on su…ìii ko ardoo on, hajoo on.
\v 13 Jogano…óon …ìe teddungal tii…óungal e giggol, sabu kuu…óe ma…ì…ìe …óen. Yo …ìuttu wonu hakkunde mon.
\v 14 Men yamirii on, yo musi…ì…ìe, hajee puy…ìe …ìen, wakkilinon aamitu…ìe …ìen, wallito…óon lo'u…ìe …ìen, wonon mu…≤…≤ii…ìe e fee won…óo woo.
\v 15 Wattanon yiila fii wota hay gooto yo…ìir bone bone, kono wa…óee soono woo ko mo∆¥∆¥i, woni non ko e hakkunde mon, woni e telen-ma won…óo woo.
\p 
\v 16 Wonee saa'i kala weltii…ìe,
\v 17 duumo…óon e toragol,
\v 18 jarnee Alla e fee kala ko woni, ko fii ko …óun woni faale Alla on fii mon, onon …ìee humondir…ìe e Iisaa Almasiihu on.
\p 
\v 19 Wota on faa…óinan Ruuhu Allaahu on.
\v 20 Wota on hayfin kongu…ói …ói Alla longini gom…óin…ìe …ìen,
\v 21 kono taskee kala huunde, jogito…óon ko mo∆¥∆¥i kon.
\v 22 Reeno…óon e bone, noone woo no o wa'i.
\p 
\v 23 Yo Alla Jom ∆Åuttu on wa…óu on yim…ìe makko ko timmi, e yo o reenu on e ba≈ã≈ãeeji …óin fow, …óun ko ruuhu mon on e wonkii mon kin e …ìandu mon ndun, fii wota on wonu felnii…ìe …≤ande ardu Iisaa Almasiihu Joomi men on.
\v 24 Ko fii on Noddu…óo on ko Sella-Findeejo, awa kadi ko on woni Timminoyoowo …óun fow.
\p 
\v 25 Musi…ì…ìe, awa toranee men menen kadi.
\v 26 Salminiree musi…ì…ìe …ìen fow hirbondiral laa…ìungal.
\v 27 Mi torike on e innde Joomi on: yo musi…ì…ìe …ìen fow jangu nduu …ìatakuru.
\p 
\v 28 Yo mo∆¥∆¥ere Iisaa Almasiihu Joomi men on wonu e mon.
